<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>扩展 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/</link><description>扩展 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MySQL瓶颈与扩展</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/mysql%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql瓶颈与扩展">MySQL瓶颈与扩展</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：MySQL单库的瓶颈在CPU、内存、磁盘IO和连接数四个维度，扩展路径从读写分离到分库分表逐步递进，每种方案都在一致性、复杂度和成本之间做权衡。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="mysql单库存在cpu内存磁盘连接数四重瓶颈扩展路径为读写分离垂直拆分水平分表分库分表">MySQL单库存在CPU、内存、磁盘、连接数四重瓶颈，扩展路径为读写分离→垂直拆分→水平分表→分库分表</h2>
<h3 id="单库瓶颈分析">单库瓶颈分析</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>瓶颈</th>
          <th>表现</th>
          <th>临时解决</th>
          <th>根本解决</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>CPU</td>
          <td>慢查询多、计算密集</td>
          <td>优化SQL、加缓存</td>
          <td>读写分离、分库</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>内存</td>
          <td>缓冲池不足、频繁换页</td>
          <td>增大内存</td>
          <td>分库分散压力</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>磁盘IO</td>
          <td>iowait高、磁盘满</td>
          <td>SSD、加索引</td>
          <td>分表、归档</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>连接数</td>
          <td>Too many connections</td>
          <td>增大max_connections</td>
          <td>连接池、分库</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="读写分离一主多从架构">读写分离：一主多从架构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">写请求 → 主库（Master）→ 异步复制 → 从库（Slave）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">读请求 → 从库1 / 从库2 / 从库N
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">复制方式：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 异步复制：主库写完即返回，延迟小但可能丢数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 半同步复制：至少一个从库确认收到binlog才返回
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 组复制（MGR）：Paxos协议，强一致性
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">延迟问题：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 主从延迟导致读取旧数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 解决方案：强制走主库（关键读）、延迟阈值告警</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="分库分表水平与垂直拆分">分库分表：水平与垂直拆分</h3>
<p><strong>垂直拆分</strong>：按业务模块拆分</p>]]></description></item><item><title>PostgreSQL 架构原理与 MySQL 对比</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/postgresql%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/postgresql%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="postgresql-架构原理与-mysql-对比">PostgreSQL 架构原理与 MySQL 对比</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：PostgreSQL 通过<strong>进程模型</strong>实现连接隔离、通过<strong>统一存储层</strong>管理数据、通过<strong>多版本并发控制（MVCC）<strong>实现无锁读写、通过</strong>丰富的索引类型和扩展体系</strong>覆盖从 OLTP 到 AI 向量的全场景，其设计哲学是&quot;扩展优先、标准兼容、企业级可靠&quot;；而 MySQL 以&quot;简单优先、性能优先&quot;著称，两者在架构模型、MVCC 实现、索引体系和扩展能力上存在根本性差异。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="postgresql-通过进程架构统一存储层mvcc-和扩展体系实现企业级可靠性">PostgreSQL 通过进程架构、统一存储层、MVCC 和扩展体系实现企业级可靠性</h2>
<h3 id="进程架构每个连接独立进程崩溃隔离优于线程模型">进程架构：每个连接独立进程，崩溃隔离优于线程模型</h3>
<h3 id="存储管理表空间--toast--页面结构大字段外置存储">存储管理：表空间 + TOAST + 页面结构，大字段外置存储</h3>
<h3 id="mvcc-与事务快照隔离--可见性规则--vacuum-清理">MVCC 与事务：快照隔离 + 可见性规则 + Vacuum 清理</h3>
<h3 id="索引体系b-tree--gin--gist--brin-覆盖全场景">索引体系：B-Tree / GIN / GiST / BRIN 覆盖全场景</h3>
<h3 id="扩展生态pgvector--postgis--citus-等插件体系">扩展生态：pgvector / PostGIS / Citus 等插件体系</h3>
<hr>
<h2 id="实现原理与关键机制">实现原理与关键机制</h2>
<h3 id="进程模型-vs-mysql-线程模型">进程模型 vs MySQL 线程模型</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">PostgreSQL 进程模型：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│              Postmaster (主进程)           │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   - 监听端口 5432                          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   - 管理所有子进程生命周期                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   - 协调崩溃恢复                           │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└──────────────────────────────────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌─────┼─────┬─────────┬─────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ▼     ▼     ▼         ▼         ▼
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  后端    后端   后端      后端       后端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  进程    进程   进程      进程       进程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  conn1   conn2  conn3    conn4      conn5
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ───────────────────────────────────────
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  每个连接 = 独立进程 (fork)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">共享内存区域（所有进程共享）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 缓冲池（Buffer Pool）     - 缓存表页和索引页
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── WAL 缓冲区                - 预写日志缓冲
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 锁表（Lock Table）        - 进程间锁协调
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 进程通信区                 - 进程间信号传递
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── 事务状态数组               - 全局事务快照</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">MySQL (InnoDB) 线程模型：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│           mysqld (单进程多线程)            │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│                                          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   主线程 ──→ 监听端口 3306                 │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │                                   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      ├──→ 连接线程池                      │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    ├── 线程 1 (conn1)             │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    ├── 线程 2 (conn2)             │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    └── 线程 N (connN)             │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │                                   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      ├──→ 后台线程                      │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    ├── IO 线程（读/写日志）        │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    ├── Purge 线程                │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │    └── Page Cleaner 线程         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      │                                   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│      └──→ 共享缓冲池（Buffer Pool）       │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│                                          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   所有线程共享同一地址空间                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└──────────────────────────────────────────┘</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>核心差异</strong>：</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>